  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Ribbit the frog astronaut runs out of spaceship fuel mid-journey, he crash-lands onto a magical floating island world. Luckily, he meets friendly villagers who guide him on a cozy, delightful adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the villagers' help, Ribbit explores various floating islands, each with unique themes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grass Island</strong>: A lovely, lush landscape perfect for gentle exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gothic Ruins Island</strong>: Mysterious and intriguing ancient structures await your discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Village Island: Cozy and peaceful, enjoy 'Retirement Life' here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.poster.avif?t=1743197534\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.webm?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.mp4?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪙 <strong>Collect & Explore</strong>: Enjoy continuous fun collecting items and interacting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/6d7df01b5460baaedb6927b725b2ab46.poster.avif?t=1743197534\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/6d7df01b5460baaedb6927b725b2ab46.webm?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/6d7df01b5460baaedb6927b725b2ab46.mp4?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚀 <strong>Pilot Your Aircraft</strong>: Freely fly between the main island (village island) and the whale island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/e3b24f683e46a56de5cfb192a716bd02.poster.avif?t=1743197534\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/e3b24f683e46a56de5cfb192a716bd02.webm?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/e3b24f683e46a56de5cfb192a716bd02.mp4?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ <strong>Relaxing Gameplay</strong>: Casual, stress-free gameplay suitable for players of all ages.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💬 <strong>Fun NPC Interactions</strong>: Engaging characters and heartwarming mini-stories enrich your exploration.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax, collect, explore, and enjoy a stress-free journey suitable for players of all ages!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Ribbit the frog astronaut runs out of spaceship fuel mid-journey, he crash-lands onto a magical floating island world. Luckily, he meets friendly villagers who guide him on a cozy, delightful adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the villagers' help, Ribbit explores various floating islands, each with unique themes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grass Island</strong>: A lovely, lush landscape perfect for gentle exploration.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gothic Ruins Island</strong>: Mysterious and intriguing ancient structures await your discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Village Island: Cozy and peaceful, enjoy 'Retirement Life' here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.poster.avif?t=1743197534\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.webm?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/b24590d10639f296f173daee2bd90ee3.mp4?t=1743197534\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪙 <strong>Collect & Explore</strong>: Enjoy continuous fun collecting items and interacting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extras/6d7df01b5460baaedb6927b725b2ab46.poster.avif?t=1743197534\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579880/extra